title: Tottenham Independent: Maisie Williams back for third dose of Doctor Who - Haringey Independent
text:
Writer Sarah Dollard confirmed that the Game Of Thrones star would be appearing once more in Face The Raven, the 10th episode of the series. Speaking on a panel at MCM London Comic Con, Sarah was prompted by showrunner Steven Moffat to tease: "It's possible Maisie will be back in episode 10." On Twitter, she confirmed the spoiler and wrote that Maisie's return had been "really difficult not to tell everyone".
 Haringey Independent.
